let default = () => {
  <>
    <Meta title="llllvvuu" description="" />
    <Layout>
      <h2>{"Journey"->React.string}</h2>
      <p>
        {"In the beginning, I only cared about solving hard problems,
        with no social purpose."->React.string}
      </p>
      <p>
        {"As I began to seek social purpose in college,
        I joined the organizing team for "->React.string}
        <a href="https://ea.mit.edu/" target="_blank">{"MIT Effective Altruism."->React.string}</a>
        {" I still only considered direct work in
        what would now be called \"deep tech\"
        as a way to achieve human flourishing."->React.string}
      </p>
      <p>
        {"Soon after I joined the \"real world\" (working on "->React.string}
        <a href="https://www.getcruise.com/" target="_blank">
          {"self-driving cars, "->React.string}
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.soundhound.com/" target="_blank">
          {"speech recognition"->React.string}
        </a>
        {", and "->React.string}
        <a href="https://www.canarymedia.com/articles/solar/solar-software-synergy-aurora-acquires-folsom-labs" target="_blank">
          {"solar design and optimization"->React.string}
        </a>
        {"), I realized that social problems,
        including "->React.string}
        <a href="https://slatestarcodex.com/2014/07/30/meditations-on-moloch/" target="_blank">
          {"coordination problems"->React.string}
        </a>
        {", were a huge bottleneck to flourishing.
        I began scoping out a pivot to the social sciences."->React.string}
      </p>
      <p>
        {"Before I could make a career move, DeFi summer happened.
        No longer is it necessary to climb up the public policy ladder
        to begin experimenting with policy - code is policy.
        With cryptonetworks forming overnight,
        I saw opportunity to test, within a much more open and agile environment,
        theories from my own reading in social science and the new ideas of cryptoeconomics
        and cryptogovernance."->React.string}
      </p>
      <p>
        {"My first production will be meta: "->React.string}
        <a href="https://atoms.org" target="_blank">
          {"coordination for research"->React.string}
        </a>
        {", including research on coordination itself."->React.string}
      </p>

    </Layout>
  </>
}
